Vasectomy gains popularity in Iran - official . Vasectomies have gained popularity in Iran with increasing numbers of operations , a health official said on Monday . Some 1 , 455 vasectomies were performed during the first half of the current Iranian year which began on March 20 , 1996 , said Hamidreza Sadeqqi - Pour , deputy for health affairs of the Medical Sciences University of Tehran . The number of operations during the same period in the previous year was 435 , he told the official Islamic Republic News Agency . 
